SEARCH
Package fooddatacentral

Class SearchQuery

java.lang.Object
fooddatacentral.SearchQuery
public class SearchQuery extends Object
Search query class utilized for the search function in FoodDataCentral. If not specified, the search will default to the following: 50 items per page, page 1, will search all fields, sort by no fields, no sort order

    • SearchQuery

      public SearchQuery(String query, int pageNumber, int pageSize, FoodSortableAttributes queryField, FoodSortableAttributes sortBy, SortOrder sortOrder)
      Generates query by setting all values manually.
      Parameters:
      query - search term, may include search operators
      pageNumber - page to return of found values
      pageSize - number of items to return per page
      queryField - what field the query will apply to
      sortBy - what to sort the returned values by
      sortOrder - what order to sort the returned values by
